	<p pid="a.13.0/1">The Government are not aware of what research is being carried out at the University of Surrey and the University of Albany in this area. The committee on toxicity of chemicals in food, consumer products and the environment keeps under review research on dioxins and polychlorinated biphenyls, which have similar toxic properties, and will consider any significant developments in the area of human health.</p>
